TX - unless you are in the Army and register from out of state.  I'm a 
TX resident and was able to register an old Mini Cooper that I bought 
from Georgia, while living in Missouri.  All I had to do was fill out 
the application and mail it to TX.  Too easy. That was less than a year ago.

